{"tid":1640271,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[求FC]]馬鞍山啲居民係咪傻撚左，竟然搏曬老命幫襯一間狗開既店舖","createTime":"2019-10-09T01:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T04:33:38.000Z","uid":17248,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4ebf78dfe9a7cb2d08f535307a509d5189bf8c","tid":1640271,"uid":17248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"有前員工爆料馬鞍山既台灣一芳水果茶既其中一個老闆係警司黎<br />\n雖然未FC佢6月之後仲有冇做<br />\n但都唔好幫襯啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔係唔記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612 721 831 新屋嶺</span></span>呀嘛<br />\n哩隻狗除時都唔知有冇申報添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠膽死想戴著香港一芳總代理既光環黎賺錢<br />\n你哩隻警司唔配呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇手足幫手FC下哩隻警司仲有冇做<br />\n有既話就麻煩Share去馬鞍山之友提醒手足唔好再幫襯啦<br />\n你地甘心比錢條差婆賺對唔對得著犧牲左既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩<br />\n願榮光歸於香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"853f0d3d0fe52a16a0a7b1093f3ccba9f28a2628","tid":1640271,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"呢間野真係好撚多人排隊"},{"pid":"31cf5075b4896a503e11ae31fe9b162a234574f4","tid":1640271,"uid":325540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:07:03.000Z","msg":"P牌幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105f1b883fd935291e0e41f7eeab01fe6b42a70a","tid":1640271,"uid":78418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:11:03.000Z","msg":"唔係澄清咗喇咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cce5d9b2d0887d931a5b359c3bf80f0e9fc18e","tid":1640271,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:14:07.000Z","msg":"黃黃藍藍難分